ck behavior; the dynamic live-model candidate harness completed without the prior plugin-discovery recursion/timeout path.\n- What was not tested: None\n\n## Tests\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner-execution.test.ts -t 'classifies GPT-5 plan-only|classifies final GPT-5 terminal-empty|rolls back persisted fallback selection' --reporter verbose`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/agents/live-model-dynamic-candidates.test.ts --reporter verbose`\n\nAlso posted the same branch-level fix context on #84814.",
